32
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,140
So let's begin with a fallacy of a claim.

33
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:35,090
A false dilemma.

34
00:01:35,090 --> 00:01:39,980
A false dilemma simply is reducing a complex issue to two issues.

35
00:01:39,980 --> 00:01:42,520
And I've got a sample text here that I'm going to read to you.

36
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,890
