00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:59,420
fund came back and it was reported on as being ethically dubious.

182
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:02,660
And so this is often been critiqued as being a red herring issue.

183
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:05,410
Because what he does is he goes through and gives himself an audit,

184
00:09:05,410 --> 00:09:08,720
and then at the end of his speech-- and television's very much in its

185
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:11,760
infancy here-- at the end of this speech he says, now people have

