00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:23,850
No one was saying that he should give back dogs.

190
00:09:23,850 --> 00:09:29,110
The were talking about campaign funds and misattribution and ethically

191
00:09:29,110 --> 00:09:30,310
dubious behavior.

192
00:09:30,310 --> 00:09:34,900
This was well before Watergate, but that was the issue, is that some saw

193
00:09:34,900 --> 00:09:42,120
that piece of evidence as an overly maudlin attempt to distract from the

194
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:44,600
key issue of inappropriate use of funds.

195
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:48,740
So you can go ahead and take a look at this clip, this small segment, as this

